OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,FSimon Harris went along to the farm in
OL,8,FSurrey.
OL,10,FFarmers say government plans for the
OL,11,Freintroduction of inheritance tax
OL,12,Fwould make their farms 'non-viable'.
OL,14,FThey are planning a protest on Tuesday
OL,15,Fnear Downing Street with farmers
OL,16,Fcoming from across the country.
