OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,FThe new rules say from April 2026,
OL,8,Finherited agricultural assets worth
OL,9,Fmore than one million pounds - which
OL,10,Fwere previously exempt - will be
OL,11,Fliable to inheritance tax at 20% which
OL,12,Fis half the normal rate.
OL,14,FThe threshold rises to #3 million for
OL,15,Fhusband and wife farmers.
OL,17,FKeith and Nellie are among the farmers
OL,18,Fworried about the return of these
OL,19,Frules.
