OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,FKeith is the fourth generation of his
OL,8,Ffamily to farm the 300 acres in
OL,9,FBrockham, Surrey.
OL,11,FThey hope to pass the cattle farm over
OL,12,Fto their children who are nine and 11,
OL,13,Fbut fear these changes may make it
OL,14,Fimpossible.
OL,16,F"It would make this a non viable
OL,17,Fbusiness," Nellie explains.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/7
