OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,F"At the moment it's viable with the
OL,8,Fland we have. We need the acreage we
OL,9,Fhave to finish and do the cattles that
OL,10,Fwe are doing and keeping both my
OL,11,Fhusband and I in a job and keeping the
OL,12,Fcountryside looing as it does.
OL,14,F"It's just putting the news out there
OL,15,Fto hang us quickly," she added.
OL,17,FThe environment secretary has said
OL,18,Fthat three quarters of farmers will
OL,19,Fpay nothing following these changes.
