OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,FSteve Reed added: "Family farming will
OL,8,Fcontinue into future generations as it
OL,9,Fshould."
OL,11,FHowever, Victoria Atkins, the shadow
OL,12,Fenvironment secretary said: "He can
OL,13,Fexplain the veracity and the accuracy
OL,14,Fof his figures next week when
OL,15,Fthousands of farmers are coming to
OL,16,FWestminster to rally against the
OL,17,Ffamily farm tax."
