OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,FThis protest was originally planned
OL,8,Ffor Trafalgar Square but has since
OL,9,Fbeen moved to Richmond Terrace in
OL,10,FWhitehall as the campaign gains more
OL,11,Fand more support.
OL,13,FOne of the organisers is Clive Bailey
OL,14,Ffrom the Farming Forum.
OL,16,F"We don't want to cause disruption,
OL,17,Fthe idea is not to bring the capital
OL,18,Fto a halt French style," he explains.
