OL,3,CLivelihood 'at risk of being
OL,4,Cdestroyed' say farmers ahead of
OL,5,Cprotest in London
OL,7,F"What we're organising is a non-
OL,8,Fdisruptive demonstration of the human
OL,9,Fside of this, we're encouraging
OL,10,Ffarmers and people in rural
OL,11,Fcommunities, small businesses affected.
OL,13,F"We may have a tractor or so there
OL,14,Fsymbolically or something like that,
OL,15,Fwe don't want farmers to come on
OL,16,Ftractors, this is not that kind of
OL,17,Fevent, the only tractors that will be
OL,18,Fo this march, we've got some
OL,19,Fchildren's on pedal tractors leading
OL,20,Ffrom the front because this is them
OL,21,Fthat it affects."
